casebody.data:
McAllister, Respondent, v. Peck et al., Appellants. (Common Pleas of New York, City and County, General Term. November, 1889.)

Argued before Larremore, C. J., and Daly and Van Hoesen, JJ

F. M. Littlefield, for appellants. B. Metzger, for respondent.

No opinion. Motion for affirmance of judgment for non-service of printed papers granted, with costs.
